                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "La poudre des astres brisés\nRoule encor par les étendues :\nMais où vont le vent des baisers\nEt l'âme des amours perdues ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Comme des étoiles, nos cœurs",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Sont faits de lumière immortelle ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Ils se brisent aux chocs vainqueurs ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mais leur poussière où donc va-t-elle ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme des étoiles, nos cœurs\nSont faits de lumière immortelle ;\nIls se brisent aux chocs vainqueurs ;\nMais leur poussière où donc va-t-elle ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Nous voyons couler notre sang",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Au bord de la nue enflammée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Dans le couchant éblouissant ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Mais où fuit sa rouge fumée ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous voyons couler notre sang\nAu bord de la nue enflammée,\nDans le couchant éblouissant ;\nMais où fuit sa rouge fumée ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Quelle brise, effleurant ces flots,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Recueille l'esprit de nos rêves,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Les délices de nos sanglots",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et l'ivresse des heures brèves ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Quelle brise, effleurant ces flots,\nRecueille l'esprit de nos rêves,\nLes délices de nos sanglots\nEt l'ivresse des heures brèves ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! dans les débris radieux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Qui font ta lumière argentée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Sous les pas tranquilles des dieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Emporte-les, ô Mer lactée !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! dans les débris radieux\nQui font ta lumière argentée,\nSous les pas tranquilles des dieux,\nEmporte-les, ô Mer lactée !"
        }
    ],
